Package se.digg.dgc.payload.v1

Class DigitalGreenCertificate

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.digg.dgc.payload.v1.DigitalGreenCertificate
  • public class DigitalGreenCertificate
extends Object
    Digital Green Certificate

    Proof of vaccination, test results or recovery according to EU eHN, version 1.0, including certificate metadata; According to 1) REGULATION OF THE EUROPEAN PARLIAMENT AND OF THE COUNCIL on a framework for the issuance, verification and acceptance of interoperable certificates on vaccination, testing and recovery to facilitate free movement during the COVID-19 pandemic (Digital Green Certificate) - https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A52021PC0130 2) Document "Value Sets for the digital green certificate as stated in the Annex ...", abbr. "VS-2021-04-14" - https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/fpfis/wikis/x/05PuKg 3) Guidelines on verifiable vaccination certificates - basic interoperability elements - Release 2 - 2021-03-12, abbr. "guidelines"
